<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Set Password</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6;">
  <h2>Hi <%= username %>,</h2>
  <p>
    You recently attempted to log in to your account. It looks like you haven't set a password yet.
    Click the button below to set your password:
  </p>
  <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">
    <a href="<%= setPasswordLink %>" style="
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-size: 16px;
    " target="_blank">Set Password</a>
  </p>
  <p>If you didn't attempt to log in, please ignore this email.</p>
  <p>Thank you,<br>Team TaskIT</p>
</body>
</html>
